text: Justice Tompkins may refer to: *Arthur S. Tompkins, a justice of the New York Supreme Court *Daniel D. Tompkins, an Associate Justice of the appellate court that was then called the Supreme Court of New York and later Vice President of the United States *George Tompkins, an Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of Missouri *Nathaniel Tompkins, an Associate Justice of the Maine Supreme Judicial Court
title: Justice Tompkins
